data.title: C Site Flank Traps for B and A
data.description: Use these B and A flank traps when your team wants to take C Site.

data.title: A Lobby Flank Trap + Cyber Cage lineup for A Main Cross
data.description: Use this Flank Trap Wire + Cyber Cage lineup for the A Main cross to condition the enemy team and make it more difficult for them to have A Main control throughout your attacking half, and / or make it easier for your team to take space in A Main.
